name: Sub Threshold XX #1
description:
This challenging session builds upon the earlier work of steady sub-threshold efforts. By challenging your ability to process lactate at near-threshold power, you will increase your exhaustion time and endurance. 



All this is achieved with a 30min steady state effort that dips briefly into the realms of VO2max.
